        <div class="wall_text"><div id="wpt-46943161_17593" class="_wall_post_cont"><div class="published_comment"><div class="wall_post_text"><a href="/wall-46943161?q=%23%D0%92%D0%B5%D1%87%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F_%D0%BF%D0%B0%D0%BC%D1%8F%D1%82%D1%8C">#Вечная_память@soldiers_of_fortune</a> <br><a href="/wall-46943161?q=%23%D0%92%D0%BE%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B5_%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BC%D1%83%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%8B">#Военные_мемуары@soldiers_of_fortune</a></div></div></div><div class="copy_quote"><div class="copy_post_header">
    <a class="copy_post_image" data-post-id="-54246568_557" data-parent-post-id="-46943161_17593" href="/vanil_samogon">
      <img src="https://pp.userapi.com/c413431/v413431717/85db/Fysg2WiBv6Q.jpg" width="40" height="40" class="copy_post_img">
